# Comparison

## 1. Which roadmap feels more personalized?

Prompt B feels more personalized because it considers my current education, existing skills, available study time, career goal, and preferred learning style.

## 2. Which roadmap would I actually follow?

Prompt B because it directly matches my goal of becoming a Data Analyst and includes projects relevant to my career.

## 3. What role did context play?

Context gave the AI information about my background, skills, and goals. Because of this, the roadmap became more realistic, practical, and tailored to my needs instead of being generic.

# Key Learnings

1. Better context produces better AI outputs.
2. AI makes fewer assumptions when given background information.
3. Personalized prompts generate more actionable plans.
4. Context Engineering is one of the most important skills in modern AI systems.
5. The same prompt can produce very different results depending on the context provided.

